      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been clearly well-cared for by its previous owners. The exterior paint still shines, though you will find a few minor rock chips and light surface scratches typical of a used vehicle. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, showing only light wear on the driver's seat bolster and no major stains or odors. It drives smoothly and has been regularly serviced, offering a dependable and attractive option for its next owner.",
